ProcDeclType = enum
  ptkProc, ptkFunc, ptkIterator, ptkConverter, ptkMethod, ptkTemplate, ptkMacro
  Source   Edit 
ProcKind = enum
  pkRegular,                ## Regular proc: `hello()`
  pkOperator,               ## Operator: `*`
  pkHook,                   ## Destructor/sink (etc.) hook: `=destroy`
  pkAssgn,                  ## Assignment proc `field=`
  pkLambda                   ## Anonymous procedure
